data TokType
Objects of type TokType represent the result of the first (lexing) pass of the input text. TokTypes are identified without any lookahead or backtracing of the input.

type TToken = (Tok, SourcePos)
Tokens are Toks with the metadata of SourcePos
type TokSt = [Tok]
Objects of TokSt are used to store the Token stack during first pass lexing.
data R_ResOp
Reserved operations which cannot be overwritten and require rearrangement during the second pass.
